com.github.rolecraftdev.profession

Class ProfessionManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.rolecraftdev.profession.ProfessionManager

  • public final class ProfessionManager
extends Object
    Groups a bunch of Professions together, to make them easier accessible and to provide additional functionality.

      • addProfession

        public boolean addProfession(Profession profession)
        Add a Profession to this ProfessionManager. Make sure its ProfessionManager is equivalent to the one it is added to, before doing so.
        Parameters:
        profession - - The Profession that should be added
        Returns:
        False if the given Profession is already contained by this Profession and thus, isn't added. True otherwise.
